# 🚀 TechShop Git Ignore Rules

# --- .NET / C# ---
bin/
obj/
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.doccache
.vs/
.vscode/

# Sensitive Files (All Folders)
**/.env
**/.env.local
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.template
appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Development.json
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# --- Others ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.bak
/tmp/

# --- Project Specific Workspace Cleanup ---
**/*.txt
**/*.log
README.md
**/README.md
InterviewGuide.md
**/InterviewGuide.md
user_audit_db.txt
**/user_audit_db.txt
build_errors.txt
